      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/4/20/13",
      "text": [
        ": \"إِذَا كَانَ اَلْعَبْدُ تَحْتَهُ أَمَةٌ فَطَلَّقَهَا تَطْلِيقَةً ثُمَّ أُعْتِقَا جَمِيعاً كَانَتْ عِنْدَهُ عَلَى تَطْلِيقَةٍ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4871 - Ḥammad narrated from al-Ḥalabi, from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"If a slave man had a bondwoman as his wife and he divorced her once, and then both of them were freed, she would remain with him on the basis of that one divorce.\""
        ]
      }
